The Grand at Midvale is your new community – situated at the heart of the cozy town of Midvale. Enjoy the safe streets, exceptional schools, and relaxing outdoor living. The Grand at Midvale finds itself in a quiet neighborhood where couples, professionals, and small families can embrace the sounds of nature. Offering 24 units, you can choose between spacious one-bedroom and two-bedroom apartments featuring Quartz Countertops*, Undermount Sinks*, Upgraded Lighting Fixtures*, and more. The community provides covered parking, additional storage, and elevators. If you’re looking for a peaceful way of living right outside of Salt Lake City, then The Grand at Midvale is just the home for you. *Select Units Only<br>
<br>
We are a pet friendly community, dogs and cats are welcome!<br>
<br>
The Grand at Midvale is located in a charming neighborhood, where the pleasant space is just a short drive away from life’s adventures. The one-and two-bedroom apartments form an accessible community with elevator support and beautiful mountain views. Outside of the neighborhood, the rest of Midvale is full of a thriving art scene, community events, extraordinary school systems, and fantastic local restaurants. And you can’t forget the abundance of outdoor recreation, including lush parks and nearby ski resorts. If you need something even more stimulating – you’re only 12 miles away from the center of Salt Lake City.<br>
